OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fthis evening and overnight with
OL,7,Fprolonged clear spells for most. A
OL,8,Fstrengthening breeze around coasts and
OL,9,Fhills. A cool night with low cloud,
OL,10,Fmist and fog patches.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAny patchy low cloud
OL,13,Fclearing then sunny spells initially.
OL,14,FCloud tending to thicken as the day
OL,15,Fprogresses ahead of rain arriving
OL,16,Flater. Another very mild day before
OL,17,Fthis.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
